Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,UgwL-u1oUYsN56t-qZ94AaABAg,,@timokaurala6657,"This is one of those rare movies that seem to get better every time you watch it. So many details in the lighting and camera work, how tight the plot is, yet how smoothly it seems to unfold, how everything seems to slot in perfectly as it wraps up. You'll watch this years from now and have a whole new appreciation for this beautifully made little movie.
