Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,UgynjJn1ShlTPAi1BWh4AaABAg,,@stevenmix3723,"I watched this reaction, because I have watched this movie a hundred times. It's about as perfect as a movie can possibly get. I was pleased that you caught on to the stunning fact that it was made during the war. In fact, right at the early years, when nobody knew what would happen yet. Fun fact, ""Play It Again Sam"" is a 1970s Woody Allen parody, based on the most misremembered line of dialogue ever.",2026-05-03T08:25:48Z,2026-05-03T08:25:48Z,1,False,0.0,2026-05-19T02:01:09.278018
