Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyO3AOnHKt8PK53Rnl4AaABAg,,@RightToLive3222,"Morroco is a corrupt country. The law and constitution is broken. 

Law and order only exists if bribes are paid. 

The court system is rigged where you always fall short of their demands. 

I was a landlord in Marrakesh. I tried to evict the tenant, the case is still active even after 4 years.

This was not a murder case. This was a case of evicting a tenant from my property. 

I would urge anyone not to invest in Morroco as the people and system is corrupt and broken.",2026-01-29T20:33:20Z,2026-01-29T20:33:20Z,0,False,2.0,2026-05-19T02:01:31.920954
