Instagram,6McQ5BmYTzc,Ugz_WSiRhg_97JADpMZ4AaABAg,,@LifeWorthBuilding,"Maybe instead of the “algorithm” not pushing your content. People are slowly starting to realize that other people don’t care about what you say or how you say it in that way. Before, they would be nice enough to give you the time of day in person because they are face to face. But now online, it’s sooo easy to ignore you. So you now have to play a mental game of “how do I get this person to stick around and hear what I have to say, and like it, and have it be relatable enough to share, and felt so moved as to make a comment”. Only then, will your video be pushed.",2026-05-18T14:43:32Z,2026-05-18T14:43:32Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-19T02:02:44.211950
